content.html: You wanna know what happens to your orders? They come to me. In your GARBAGE! I could hang myself with all the bad Amazon Basics neckties I found at the dump! The avarice never ends! "I want golf clubs. I want diamonds. I want a pony I can ride, get bored and sell to make glue."
